## 

1. GitHub 
2.  Git
3.  Node.js

##  GitHub 

1.  GitHub 
2.  `< GitHub >.github.io`  `github.io` 


##  Hexo

HexoHexo NodeJSHexo
1.  shift+  `Git Bash Here` 
2. Git Bash `npm install -g hexo-cli`  hexo 
3.  `npx hexo init`  hexo 
> 
4. `npx hexo g`
5. `hexo s`
[http://localhost:4000](http://localhost:4000)
> Hexo[ | Hexo](https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/)

> GitHubGitHub


>  GitHub 

##  Hexo  GitHub

1. `Git Bash` hexo`Git`

```shell
npm install hexo-deployer-git --save
```

2. ,`_config.yml`,`deploy`:

>  `hexo-deployer-git` GitHub


```markdown
deploy:
	type: git
	repository: https://github.com/GitHub/GitHub.github.io.git  #
	branch: main #
```

>  GitHub  deploy

> ``



![](https://github.com/zhchhe/image-bed/raw/3e0ac1c410ed2719a53537b2296d13ea5c069e5a/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87/Snipaste_2023-06-06_21-58-26.png)

3.  `git bash` 

```shell
hexo clean   # db.json  public
hexo g       # public (g generate )
hexo d       #public(d deploy )
```

4.  `https://xxx.github.io` 

`hexo s`  [http://localhost:4000](http://localhost:4000) GitHub

5.  `https://xxx.github.io` GitHub

![](https://github.com/zhchhe/image-bed/raw/3e0ac1c410ed2719a53537b2296d13ea5c069e5a/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87/Snipaste_2023-06-06_21-58-48.png)

  `https://xxx.github.io`
